{"tid":2372437,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國對沖基金巨頭Elliott Management將關閉香港辦事處","createTime":"2021-01-19T15:50:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T11:51:01.000Z","uid":225931,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4d10294ebd9ca20463e974c94d3a4f4265ecf4d7","tid":2372437,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T15:50:17.000Z","msg":"據英國《金融時報》19日報導，美國對沖基金巨頭埃利奧特管理公司（Elliott Management）將關閉香港辦事處。<br />\n<br />\n 埃利奧特管理公司由保羅&middot;辛格爾（Paul Singer）創建於1977年，進入香港已有15年的時間。 該公司現決定將香港團隊轉移至倫敦和東京的辦事處，後者將成為其在亞洲的唯一總部。<br />\n<br />\n 一份發送給投資者的備忘錄表示，&ldquo;與埃利奧特的長期規劃流程一致，我們將關閉香港辦事處的交易和投資活動，2021年1月1日起生效，將把現有的亞洲（ 除日本外）投資頭寸和新的情境交易和投資的負責團隊轉移至倫敦辦事處。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"de3c5448bfce0834515eb2968472cdbc87c3f42a","tid":2372437,"uid":5178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T15:50:44.000Z","msg":"利好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c089fd4c0b8975ddc5f08ee273920050d2380de2","tid":2372437,"uid":38904,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T15:51:06.000Z","msg":"賣咗bea就走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8c22913a027611c117d03da3ec9774278e69e1c","tid":2372437,"uid":217049,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T15:51:24.000Z","msg":"東京都收到香港皮嘅年代<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4be561da211e44fc1cefcc6bca3751e0204722c6","tid":2372437,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T15:51:36.000Z","msg":"爭唔過同業咪走囉 又賴香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebd64b44cefa9b522083538d92e779fb1aaac78d","tid":2372437,"uid":277992,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T15:51:48.000Z","msg":"睇唔到有外國公司撤離香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f696cfee28d980f30b3d9dde8dffbcc6fac